### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّهُمُ ٱتَّبَعُوا۟ مَآ أَسْخَطَ ٱللَّهَ وَكَرِهُوا۟ رِضْوَٰنَهُۥ فَأَحْبَطَ أَعْمَـٰلَهُمْ</span>

### English

This is because they follow whatever displeases Allah and hate whatever pleases Him, so He has rendered their deeds void.